race.description: Melbourne Cup Day Here Tuesday 4th November
race.comment: THEHORSEMAN (3) won by a space first up for the new stable and then improved again winning easily this grade finishing powerfully. Fitter again and the longer sprint will hold no fears. COLLECTIVE (9) settled last from a wide barrier and couldn't have been more impressive beaten a whisker first up. Has more to give and tumbles in weight this grade and that brings her right into it. BIGDAYONIT (7) is hard to catch but he has ability. He led beaten 1L at Belmont two back over this distance and will position forward from an inside barrier. Faithfull sticking aboard is a positive. DIVINE INANNA (10) seeks the hat-trick and also stays down in the weights. She deserves consideration as well.
